Slide 5: Monitoring and Analysis
Real-Time Monitoring: Utilize AWS Container Insights for detailed performance metrics and monitoring of EKS clusters.
Metrics: Track CPU, memory usage, and network activity of pods and nodes.
AWS CloudWatch Logs: Capture application logs for deeper insights.
Log Insights: Use CloudWatch Logs Insights to analyze logs and troubleshoot issues.
Post-Experiment Analysis: Evaluate the impact of the EC2 instance termination on application performance and resilience based on collected metrics and logs.
